Introduction

D-ONE is a five-member boy group under Mainbase Entertainment. They debuted on November 26, 2022, with the single "Torch."

On August 27, 2023, D-ONE debuted in Japan with the single "One Dance." However, two days later, on August 29, Doyul left the group due to personal reasons. On November 27, Sejin joined the group.
